description.plain: Khalif Malik Ibn Shaman Brown (born June 7, 1993 in Inglewood, California), better known by his stage name Swae Lee, is an American rapper from Tupelo, Mississippi. He is one half of the duo Rae Sremmurd alongside his brother Slim Jxmmi.
